Uses of Package
simulation

  • Packages that use simulation 
    Package Description
    colony
    Package that gives the methods and utilities to perform a simulation of a specific population.
    events
    Package that extends an event to a specific type.
    simulation
    Package that implements the stochastic simulation based on event, provided for extension depending of a population.
  • Classes in simulation used by colony 
    Class and Description
    Events
    Abstract Class where an event of the simulation is defined (to be added in the PEC) All the events have the event time attribute in common, and so when the object of this class is created, the event time is schedule (for the given time).
    Simulation
    Abstract class where is define a Stochastic Simulation based on the event occurence.
